Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
readWriteLefCh...ncoloredShapes(25.10)  readWriteLefCh...ncoloredShapes(25.10)

Name
       readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes

Syntax
        readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes {pin_only | on | off}

       Type: enum

       Default: off

       Specifies  whether  to  check  for  uncolored LEF PIN and OBS shapes on
       multi-mask routing layers when reading or writing  LEF  files.  If  the
       check is on, LEF read or write commands will error out if there are any
       uncolored  routing layer shapes (cut layers are not checked). If set to
       pin_only, only check LEF PIN shapes and ignore LEF OBS shapes.

              * During write_lef_abstract, if the  tool  finds  any  uncolored
                physical pin and if readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes is set to
                on,  the  tool will print an error message, and will not write
                out uncolored shapes to the LEF file. However, if readWriteLe-
                fCheckUncoloredShapes is set to off, the tool will  not  check
                the uncolored object and dump all physical pins into the macro
                lef. In this case, the tool does not print any error message.

              * When the tool reads the LEF file and finds any uncolored macro
                pin, and if readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes is set to on, the
                tool  will print an error message and only read colored shapes
                into the design. However, if  readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes
                is  set  to  off, the tool will not check the uncolored object
                and will read the definition of all macros into the design. In
                this case, the tool does not print any error message.

       The readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes global controls  the  behavior  of
       following commands or flow:

              * write_lef_abstract

              * restoreDesign and init design flow

              * replaceLefMacro

       readWriteLefCheckUncoloredShapes  does not impact write_lef_library and
       read/write oa tech.

Related Information
              * replaceLefMacro

              * restoreDesign

              * write_lef_abstract

              * write_lef_library

